data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE @ 2.375%!  PI is $1304.46 *** This Beautiful Spacious Home is located in the desirable Magnolia Park gated community.  Open floor plan offers 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 bathrooms and a tandem oversized 3 car garage.  The first floor is a dining room, laundry room, spacious island kitchen and family room combination featuring granite counters, 42" wood cabinets, stainless appliances, and a walk-in pantry. Upstairs is a bonus /playroom and an open computer workspace.  The Master is huge and features a double sink vanity, bathtub, walk-in shower and large walk-in closet.  Second bedroom is en suite with bathroom.  All rooms are generous in size.  No carpet, tile first floor and all wet rooms and Life Proof laminate upstairs. Both AC units replaced and exterior repainted within the last 3 years.  The lot is semiprivate with no homes directly in back.  Community maintains the lawn and landscaping and irrigation is well water.  Fantastic location close to shopping, restaurants and easy access to I-75, the Selmon Expressway, MacDill and downtown Tampa.
